    <summary>Put a website on maintenance mode, whitelist IPs, and block dev and staging websites from general visitors.</summary>
    <description>Brief Description: Put a website on maintenance mode, whitelist IPs, and block dev and staging websites from general visitors.&#xD;
&#xD;
Detailed Description: This extension can be used for the following three purposes:&#xD;
&#xD;
1) Put a Magento website on maintenance mode where the live website goes down and only certain IP numbers can view it. Setting a website on Maintenance Mode is useful during deployments.&#xD;
&#xD;
2) Show visitors a banner saying that your website will be undergoing maintenance from this date to that date.&#xD;
&#xD;
3) Use this extension to block visitors&#x2002;&#x2002;from accessing your dev and staging environments. &#xD;
Enjoy!</description>
    <notes>This extension can put a website on maintenance mode, whitelist IPs, and block dev and staging websites from general visitors.</notes>
